<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1073 ṇḍagunēṁṭi Uttarāyaṇasaṁkrāntināṁḍu ṟoṁppiceṛvula prōlināyaku koḍku mallināyaku mudiseli bētanabō<unclear>yuṇḍu</unclear> tama ta
<lb n="2" break="no"/>llidaṁḍrulaku dharmmuvugā koṭyadona tribhuvanamallaśrīkēśavadēvaraku Ākhaṇḍadīpamunaku beṭṭina velleḍlu Ēṁ<unclear>bhbha</unclear>yēnu pedda<unclear>nanne</unclear>bōyini koḍku pinnananne vīni<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> jēkoni tana putrā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nupautrikamu Ācaṁdrārkkatārakamuga Akaṇḍadīpamunaku nitya māneṁḍu neyi pōyaṁgalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā yō harēti vasundharā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> ṣaṣṭirvvarṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭāyāṁ jāyatē krimi [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
</p>

